## ğŸ›  Common CI/CD Tools (name-dropping helps ğŸ˜‰)

* **CI:** Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, CircleCI
* **CD:** Jenkins, ArgoCD, Spinnaker
* **Others:** Docker, Kubernetes, AWS CodePipeline

